data.description: Seller Financing Available!! Welcome to a remarkable property in a great Georgetown location. Nestled on 6.79 acres, this property features a 2,188 sq ft, 4-bed, 2.5-bath home and a 50x30 workshop with electric, offering diverse possibilities. While it may need some care, this hidden gem has enormous potential and a low tax rate at 1.5182. With 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, spread across 2,188 square feet, this home is perfect for families seeking space and flexibility. The main level boasts a primary bedroom for convenient single-level living, while secondary bedrooms are upstairs. Updates include a new 2022 HVAC unit and a 2021 water heater, and the roof was recently repaired, ensuring peace of mind. Animal lovers will find a barn with 3 stalls, perfect for donkeys, goats, or horses. The 1,500+ square feet workshop warehouse, complete with two 12-foot roll-up doors and a massive second level, offers endless possibilities and equipped with a 220 electric, and water can easily be connected.The property includes a stock pond for a picturesque setting. Light deed restrictions provide flexibility to shape the land. Three gates ensure easy access. The property presents an exceptional opportunity to subdivide into one-acre parcels. With a tranquil setting, it's only 10 miles from Lake Georgetown, 20 minutes to downtown, and under 40 minutes to the Apple Campus and Domain. Close proximity to essentials like HEB, Costco, gas stations, and nearby parks makes this location one of the reasons Georgetown is the fastest-growing city in America.
